commentary: Usman Shinwari to Gunathilaka, no run Sarfaraz has appealed for obstruction the field. Length ball angling in, Gunathilaka was moving towards the leg side, drops it at his feet and looks for the single, Shinwari charges in towards the ball and there is a bit of a collision as he tries to reach for the ball. Sarfaraz is not happy and has appealed. The soft signal is not out. Replays confirm Gunathilaka had no idea where the ball was and was simply going for the run when he found Shinwari in his way. Not out, says third umpire

commentary: Shadab Khan to Gunathilaka, no run length ball down the leg side, goes for the flick but misses. An appeal for caught-behind by Sarfaraz, Aleem Dar says wide but Sarfaraz wants to review it. Replays show it brushed the thigh pad but no bat at all. Pakistan lose their review.
